{"tid":1696231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［跪求］尚德A停車場車cam","createTime":"2019-11-06T05:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T14:53:04.000Z","uid":206152,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf1d167aef51c890d72c7ee6d0b8950e88d78b1","tid":1696231,"uid":206152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/txeaRwh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtxeaRwh.png&h=30913ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要求尚德A停車場車cam(近將軍澳運動場停車場)<br />\n跪求大家如果知到身邊有朋友係車而且停泊係尚德A停車場<br />\n介唔介幫手問一問佢可唔可以比車cam比尚德榮仔(葉嘉榮尚德社區主任)<br />\n每一個車cam對成件事都好重要，麻煩咁多位share出去比多啲人知<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時間：0030-0200（2019-11-04）<br />\n地點：尚德A停車場2樓-3樓</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聯絡榮仔方法：<br />\n1 Telegram: @ST_Wing<br />\n2 Email: kelvinyipsoc@gmail.com<br />\n3 Whatsapp: 6150 6333</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bad3f4a9f1dfddbe1e58eb6e3925f3ba4952c2f5","tid":1696231,"uid":206152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"再推呀"},{"pid":"cef09a8f1584b11c43c762d5e65cc1c94b0bf30d","tid":1696231,"uid":206152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:08:56.000Z","msg":"唔好比何妖分散視線呀<br />\n推上熱門呀"},{"pid":"02ecc2c3b78c0ee92e1513fcf1cb6a2f15c6403c","tid":1696231,"uid":206152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"140a4274bd4230fcea7e58885b94d73ea8dabc3a","tid":1696231,"uid":206152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d0a848e7ef51f47a6fd0e56ecab464252e255a37","tid":1696231,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推推推"},{"pid":"3